# Project #12 - Project Plan

## Business Goals
* Write an essential project plan for a web development project
* Project goals should be defined for Project #13


### Essential Project Plan Content

Document your plan to answer these key questions

* Requirements
    * Primary goal
    * Priorities - Time, Money, Function
    * Top 10 objectives
    * Customer interactions
* Design
    * Pages
    * Page layout
    * Content creation
    * Visual appearance
* Code
    * Code milestones
    * Reuse plan
    * Learning plan
    * Schedule
* Test
    * Acceptance criteria
    * Issue tracking
    * Reviews
    * Release criteria


## Project Requirements

### Source Code
* Publish your Git Repository link on your home page
* Create your page at "your-domain/docs/ProjectPlan.md"
* Use your page template built on Bootstrap to create a new page
* Commit all of your code to your Github repository


### Test Your Code
* Test the simple page before your put anything interesting in it
* Send your files to Bluehost using FileZilla


## Requirements

### Technical
* Page is located at correct URL (your-domain/docs/ProjectPlan.md)
* All pages validate HTML and CSS and links
* All JavaScript widgets work
* All links work properly
* Other pages are working properly

### Business
* Page shows required business content
* Page is beautiful
* Business message is clear and compelling
* Page shows marketing carousel with photos
* Overall impression is professional

